# MPSeekCommandEventType.beginSeeking

**Case**

Indicates the external media player began seeking.

## Declaration

```swift
case beginSeeking
```

## Event types

- **MPSeekCommandEventType.endSeeking**: Indicates the external media player stopped seeking.
